To keep your python environment sane, I recommend doing this in a virtualenv [1].

To use:
* hg clone http://hg.mozilla.org/users/clegnitto_mozilla.com/mozillapulse
* python mozillapulse/setup.py develop
* hg clone http://hg.mozilla.org/automation/pulsebuildmonitor
* python pulsebuildmonitor/setup.py develop

Then clone this repo and run:
* python harvester.py

[1]:http://pypi.python.org/pypi/virtualenv

